These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, electronic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, animation
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the fan of electronic is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | punk |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Movie-Genre     | satire     | animation      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, tomato
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating zucchini is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Food   | tomato | zucchini  |
| Flower     | orchid   | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, amber
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, punk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person who likes amber is in an even position##4
2. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Color         | coral   | amber  |
| Music-Genre   | punk | trance  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

