.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, pop
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
City: boston, nizza
1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the fan of electronic is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Music-Genre          | electronic | pop |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| City     | nizza       | boston      |

