.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, japanese
1. the japanese is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the canadian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
3. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Beverage    | lemonade | cola     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Nationality   | japanese | canadian    |

